Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On top of that, he put prices on \Nthe heads of Luffy and 11 others,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now they're being hunted \Nby all the citizens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the Straw Hats fighting \Nthe Don Quixote Family fiercely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Law are heading \Nto the Royal Palace!{\i0}
